  "_purpose": "Detecta patologias del inmueble (humedades, grietas, instalaciones obsoletas) a partir de fotos. Webhook publico que recibe imagenes; llama a Vision LLM (claude/gpt-4-vision); persiste cada finding en pathology_findings con severity + cost_min/max + recommended_action; si severity=critical o affects_safety=true envia alerta inmediata al arquitecto.",
  "_triggers": "POST /webhook/pathology-detect (con archivos imagen + project_id)",
  "_persists_to": "pathology_findings (project_id, type, severity, description, cost_min, cost_max, affects_safety, recommended_action)",
  "_alerts_when": "severity=critical OR affects_safety=true -> Send Alert via Gmail al architect_email",
